{"type":"answer","id":28668,"parentType":"question","parentId":5411,"uid":6737,"contents":"卫星影像的畸变是很正常的，尤其是容易产生温度差的地方，例如水面和陆地的交界处，分水岭等地方。光从影像资料肯定是无法判断是否已经出现了严重隐患。<br>\n<br>\n但是三峡大坝的安全应该的确存在很大问题，三峡库区的蓄水已经足以影响到重力场改变，本身就会造成地震。<br>\n<br>\n真的是该拆，但是拆了很折中共面子，如果中共不倒台，我推测最终结局是大坝会出很大事故，然后推给地震之类的东西，成功摔锅，然后以地形已发生了严重改变为由拆除剩余部分，最后再说重建时间待定，留给后人处理。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://ars.els-cdn.com/content/image/1-suntrusted fake 2049bbs/1-s2.0-S1674984718300582-gr2.jpg</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n\n</a><div class=\"meta clearfix\"><a href=\"https://ars.els-cdn.com/content/image/1-suntrusted fake 2049bbs/1-s2.0-S1674984718300582-gr2.jpg</a>\t\t</div>\n\t\t<!-- end 回答 -->\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\" mod-footer\"=\"\">\n<span class=\"aw-small-text pull-right\">2019-07-08</span>\n\n<span class=\"operate aw-vote-ui\">\n</span></a><a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"agree disabled\">\n<i class=\"icon icon-agree\"></i> <b class=\"count\">1</b>\n</a>\n\n\n<span class=\"operate\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"toggle_disscusion($(this));\" class=\"aw-add-comment\" data-id=\"28668\" data-type=\"answer\" data-comment-count=\"5\"><i class=\"icon icon-comment\"></i> 5</a>\n</span>\n\n<div class=\"more-operate\">\n<a href=\"/vote/log/item_type-answer__item_id-28668\" class=\"aw-small-text\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><i class=\"icon icon-users\"></i></a>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box\" style=\"display:none\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-list\"></div>\n\n<a class=\"aw-load-more-content\">\n<span>更多</span>\n</a>\n\n<form action=\"/question/ajax/save_answer_discussion/answer_id-28668\" method=\"post\" onsubmit=\"return false\">\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box-main\">\n<textarea class=\"aw-comment-txt autosize form-control\" rows=\"2\" name=\"message\" placeholder=\"讨论一下...\"></textarea>\n<div class=\"aw-comment-box-btn\">\n<span class=\"pull-right\">\n<a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"btn btn-mini btn-success\" onclick=\"sub